%b%G%b is a utility allowing IRC users to receive global
messages from network administrators. To use the following
commands, type: %b/msg %G <command>%b. For more information
on a specific command, type:
%b/msg %G help <command>%b.

    MOTD       Display the current logon news
%+a%b* * * *%b
%+a%bAdministrator commands%b
%+a    GNOTE      Send global notices to users
%+a    GCHANNOTE  Send global notices to channels
%+a    GMEMO      Send global memos to users
%+a    GCMEMO     Send global memos to channels
